Interface IPokemon

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICard
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPokemon, ElectricPokemon, FightingPokemon, FirePokemon, GrassPokemon, PsychicPokemon, WaterPokemon

    public interface IPokemon
extends ICard
    Common interface for all the types of Pokemon. Every Pokemon have an Id, hp, energies and attacks associated.
